     CLR         $BSRY1    DIV  @DAY1     BBB    101
     CLR         BBB       ADD  0.9       $BSRY2  90
     CLR         $CSRY1    DIV  @DAY2     CCC    101
     CLR         CCC       ADD  0.9       $CSRY2  90
     CLR         $DSRY1    DIV  @DAY0     DDD    101
     CLR         DDD       ADD  0.9       $DSRY2  90
     C*
